rsing so higher-level modules can parse requests, responses, headers, and related protocol data efficiently.\\\",\\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_3/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"akka-protobuf-v3 is Akka's shaded copy of the Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\\\",\\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"akka-protobuf-v3 is Akka's shaded copy of the Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\\\",\\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:28:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"akka-protobuf-v3 is Akka's shaded copy of the Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\\\",\\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_2.13/index.json:46:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"akka-protobuf-v3 is Akka's shaded copy of the Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\\\",\\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-http_3/index.json:5:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/com/typesafe/akka/akka-http_3/$version$/akka-http_3-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-http_3/index.json:8:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"h