uced (`stats/com.typesafe.akka/akka-http_3/10.6.0-M1/execution-metrics.json`).\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `forge/logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-http_3:10.6.0-M1/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-10T11-25-35-796873Z.log`\n- `forge/logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-http_3:10.6.0-M1/metadata-fix/codex.log`\n- `forge/logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-http_3:10.6.0-M1/post-gen/pi-post-gen-2026-06-10T11-23-58-972908Z.log`\n- `stats/com.typesafe.akka/akka-http_3/10.6.0-M1/execution-metrics.json`\n\nNext steps:\n1. Complete the Akka native metadata for config resources and config-driven reflective loads used by `ActorSystem` startup, then rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.typesafe.akka:akka-http_3:10.6.0-M1`.\n2. Verify the generated `Akka_http_3Test.scala` against the final metadata changes so the five native tests pass without removing coverage.\n3. Regenerate metrics and confirm `stats/com.typesafe.akka/akka-http_3/10.6.0-M1/stats.json` is produced with dynamic-access coverage before resubmitting."}}
